## LAW 8: GREP BOTH SIDES TO FIND MISMATCHES
When client/server or multi-component systems don't connect:
```powershell
# What does one side send?
grep "emit.*event_name" server_code/

# What does other side expect?
grep "event_name" client_code/
```
Pattern: When one side works but the other is stuck â†’ MISMATCH. Grep both sides, compare exact strings.

